reviews.text: It used to be our favourite Cantonese restaurant in Central, but dinner tonight was quite disappointing. Ordered a lobster in supreme soup sauce. While the lobster was steamed perfectly, the sauce was just lukewarm. Also ordered a braised black mushrooms with tofu. The whole dish was fairly cold by the time it was served, and it was fairly greasy. Food quality seems to have degraded over our last few visits.
Good quality dimsum. Easy to get a table when  compared to Maxims at City Hall.
Quality of food are good. With many choices.  All staff are polite and efficient.  However a little bit noisy  if with many customers due to congested environment.

result.name: 怡翠軒

reviews.text: 這是一間美心集團成員，價錢中上，食物有一定水準。點心是即日製作，是新鮮感的，蝦餃是我每次必選的，螺片配海蜇很清爽，但上星期試醬油炒飯，則鹹了一點。整體上是有水準的，服務員招呼很好，屬有求必應，值得推介。
位於中環怡和大厦地庫，招呼很好，點心精緻，有乳豬沙律，鮑魚疍達，燕窩疍達，特别系芝麻卷，木桶豆府花，炒粉麵也不錯。
